<function>

access:   public

name: template

param: string, $name

return: string

</function>

Returns the path to the requested template script.

* Parameters:

 * string //$name//: The template name to look for in the template path.

* Returns string: The full path to the template script.

Used inside a template script like so:

<code>
include $this->template($name);
</code>